#

Mushroom Barley Soup

45 min
$10
180 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianHigh FiberLow Fat

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

Comfort FoodSoupHealthy

Description

A warm and hearty mushroom barley soup that's both filling and nourishing, perfect for a cozy meal.

Ingredients

  • mushrooms: 2 cups, sliced
  • barley: 1 cup
  • carrots: 1 cup, diced
  • celery: 1 cup, diced
  • onion: 1, chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • vegetable broth: 6 cups
  • bay leaves: 2
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • thyme: 1 teaspoon
